										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<span class="span-reading-time rt-reading-time" style="display: block;"><span class="rt-label rt-prefix">Reading Time: </span> <span class="rt-time"> 3</span> <span class="rt-label rt-postfix">minutes</span></span>
<p>Ruth and Gehrig. Shaq and Kobe. Brady and Gronk. </p>



<p>There have been many great duos in the history of professional sports, but perhaps none was greater than Michael Jordan and Scottie Pippen.</p>



<p>Over the course of their eleven seasons together, Jordan and Pippen led the Chicago Bulls to six championships and collaborated on countless highlight reel plays.</p>



<p>Now, two of the most famous names in sports history are making headlines once again &#8212; but not in a way that anyone predicted.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="778" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-1024x778.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-459200" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-1024x778.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-300x228.jpg 300w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-768x583.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-1536x1167.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-735x558.jpg 735w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-335x254.jpg 335w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-347x264.jpg 347w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-520x395.jpg 520w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-640x486.jpg 640w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-960x729.jpg 960w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603-1080x820.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2022/09/GettyImages-1170632603.jpg 1943w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption>Michael Jordan and Scottie Pippen during their heyday on the Chicago Bulls. (Photo via Getty)</figcaption></figure>



<p></p>



<p>According to a <a href="https://www.tmz.com/2022/09/27/larsa-pippen-marcus-jordan-dating-video-pda/">new report </a>from TMZ, Scottie&#8217;s ex-wife Larsa Pippen has been spending a lot of time with Michael&#8217;s 31-year-old son Marcus.</p>



<p>The possible couple was first seen hanging out in Miami together over a week ago.</p>



<p>Then, this past weekend Larsa and Scottie were spotted again, this time canoodling &#8212; yes, canoodling! &#8212; at the Rolling Loud festival in NYC.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"></figure>



<p></p>



<p>Witnesses say Pippen and Jordan looked as though they were about to hook up on something much more intimate than an alley-oop.</p>



<p>The two were close by each other&#8217;s side all night, dancing together and leaning up against one another between songs.</p>



<p>At one point, Larsa reportedly started to go in for a kiss but then thought better of it.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><figcaption>Larsa Pippen is rocking giant sunglasses in this photo. (Photo via Instagram)</figcaption></figure>



<p>In all likelihood, Larsa put on the brakes simply because she and Marcus are not yet ready to confirm that they&#8217;re dating/hooking up/whatever.</p>



<p>It could be that she and Marcus would simply prefer to control the narrative themselves.</p>



<p>But it&#8217;s also possible that they&#8217;re worried about what the elder Jordan will have to say about all of this.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><figcaption>Michael Jordan is a living legend. Few human beings genuinely deserve that description. (Photo via Getty)</figcaption></figure>



<p>After all, at 48, Larsa is 17 years Marcus&#8217; senior, a fact that might give Michael pause.</p>



<p>Of course, His Airness is more likely to object on the basis that Larsa was previously married to his colleague and close friend.</p>



<p>Scottie and Larsa just finalized their divorce in 2021, though the couple were on and off for several years leading up to the legal end of their marriage.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="680" height="1024" src="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-680x1024.jpg" alt="Scottie Pippen and Larsa Pippen at the Derby" class="wp-image-244475" srcset="https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-680x1024.jpg 680w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-199x300.jpg 199w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-768x1156.jpg 768w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-1021x1536.jpg 1021w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-1361x2048.jpg 1361w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-735x1106.jpg 735w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-223x335.jpg 223w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-231x347.jpg 231w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-346x520.jpg 346w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-425x640.jpg 425w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-510x768.jpg 510w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-638x960.jpg 638w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-718x1080.jpg 718w, https://cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com/uploads/2016/10/scottie-pippen-and-larsa-pippen-at-the-derby-scaled.jpg 1701w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px" /><figcaption>Scottie and Larsa Pippen in happier times. (Photo via Getty)</figcaption></figure>



<p>Still, Michael would probably prefer that Marcus date someone who was <em>never</em> married to one of his teammates!</p>



<p>In recent years, of course, Larsa has made a name for herself as a star of <em>The Real Housewives of Miami </em>and a close friend of the Kardashians.</p>



